{"id":18073,"date":"2022-12-31T04:29:52","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:29:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:29:52","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:29:52","slug":"bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\/","title":{"rendered":"Bugatti Chiron Profilee \u2013 si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ed9c nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>M\u1eabu si\u00eau xe c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n trong 2 n\u0103m, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2\/2023.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Veyron, Chiron \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong su\u1ed1t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.  Profilee l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc Chiron \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ecf.  Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 500 chi\u1ebfc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t n\u00ean Profil\u00e9e ch\u1ec9 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t 1 chi\u1ebfc cho th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Profil\u00e9e ra \u0111\u1eddi khi c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Bugatti y\u00eau c\u1ea7u nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sang s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 Chiron Pur Sport v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0.  nh\u01b0 c\u00e1nh gi\u00f3 sau c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Chiron Profilee.  \u1ea2nh: Bugatti\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" title=\"bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi-300x193.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi-600x386.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Chiron Profilee.  \u1ea2nh: Bugatti<\/p>\n<p>  <img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_567_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_567_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_166_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_166_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_83_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_83_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_419_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_419_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_203_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_203_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_401_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_401_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_644_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_644_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_46_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_46_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_923_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_923_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_3_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_3_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_80_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_80_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_734_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_734_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_836_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_836_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_234_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_234_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672425363_306_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\" title=\"1672425363_306_bugatti-chiron-profilee-sieu-pham-doc-nhat-the-gioi\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">So v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n Pur Sport, b\u1ea3n Profil\u00e9e lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00e1nh gi\u00f3 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00eda sau, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1nh l\u01b0\u1edbt gi\u00f3 nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n, tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 li\u1ec1n m\u1ea1ch h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap xe b\u00e1m \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 380 km\/h.  \u1ede ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, xe c\u00f3 c\u00e1c khe h\u00fat gi\u00f3 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Chiron ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh m\u00f3ng ng\u1ef1a r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00fat nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed h\u01a1n v\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t.  Lu\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a nh\u1edd b\u1ed9 chia ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap t\u0103ng l\u1ef1c h\u01b0\u1edbng xu\u1ed1ng \u1edf ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u xe.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u01a1 h\u1ecdc, l\u00f2 xo c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo c\u1ee9ng h\u01a1n 10% so v\u1edbi Pur Sport v\u00e0 tr\u1ee5c sau c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng s\u00e1ng g\u1ea7m h\u01a1n 50% gi\u00fap xe c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1m \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n khi v\u00e0o cua.  Bugatti cho bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Chiron.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Xe v\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 8 l\u00edt W16, 4 b\u1ed9 t\u0103ng \u00e1p, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 1.479 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c, k\u00e9m h\u01a1n m\u1ee9c 1.578 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c tr\u00ean Centodieci hay Super Sport 300+.  V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c t\u1eeb 0-100 km\/h trong 2,3 gi\u00e2y v\u00e0 0-200 km\/h trong 5,5 gi\u00e2y, Chirno Profil\u00e9e l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c nhanh nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u200b\u200btr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay.  T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 380 km\/h, cao h\u01a1n 30 km\/h so v\u1edbi Pur Sport.  Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 truy\u1ec1n c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ng\u1eafn 15% so v\u1edbi Chiron Sport.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u01a1n xanh Argent Atlantique, trong khi ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng s\u1ee3i carbon Bugatti Blu Royal.  Trong khi n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng da d\u1ec7t, v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 2.500 m\u00e9t d\u1ea3i da.  Gh\u1ebf da Gris Rafale v\u00e0 Xanh \u0111\u1eadm v\u1edbi in ch\u00e2n b\u00f4ng \u201cAir Parade\u201d.  Bugatti c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00eam l\u1edbp kh\u1ea3m khung anot h\u00f3a m\u00e0u \u0111en \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb ch\u1eef vi\u1ebft Profil\u00e9e.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">V\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3, c\u00f4ng ty \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 xe h\u01a1i RM Sotheby\u2019s s\u1ebd b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 chi\u1ebfc xe v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m 2023 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng l\u00e0m t\u1eeb thi\u1ec7n.  V\u1edbi m\u1eabu Pur Sport gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u1edf 60 chi\u1ebfc, gi\u00e1 3,6 tri\u1ec7u USD m\u1ed7i chi\u1ebfc, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia xe h\u01a1i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1eb1ng Profil\u00e9e m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 3,6 tri\u1ec7u USD.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Minh Qu\u00e2n<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u1eabu si\u00eau xe c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n trong 2 n\u0103m, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2\/2023. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Veyron, Chiron \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong su\u1ed1t v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. Profilee l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc Chiron \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":17293,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18073"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-js